Output ../assets/demo/phatom.gif

Require orrery-bin

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 32
Set Width 1200
Set Height 1200

Hide
Type "source ~/.orrery/activate.sh"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "orrery exit"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "orrery run claude"
Sleep 0.5s
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "/orrery:phantom work"
Sleep 2s
Enter
Sleep 15s
